<br>
Note however that 20 weapon 50 CD is definitely gimping yourself.  It is in no way equivalent to 50 weapon 20 CD for damage output - or at least this WAS true 6 months ago when I last investigated.<br>
<br>
Has Sanya officially retraced this bogus statement?  Has anyone logged damage for high weapon low CD vs low weapon high CD recently?<br>
